(bags rustle)

34:07.546 --> 34:09.146
(items clatter)

34:14.253 --> 34:16.720
(sniffles) you killed her,
right... Aaron?

34:16.722 --> 34:18.622
You killed flora?

34:21.460 --> 34:23.360
- It's just you and me now.

