the path?

36:44.203 --> 36:45.701
- Hey, hey, mac!
Mac, you're cutting out.

36:45.737 --> 36:49.539
<i> Wait! Hey mac!</i>
<i> You're cutting out, you--</i>

36:49.674 --> 36:52.108
(grunts in pain)

36:54.746 --> 36:56.279
Oh...

