(grunts in pain)

37:54.439 --> 37:56.639
Oh, god!

37:56.708 --> 37:59.242
(short, sharp breaths)

38:01.713 --> 38:03.713
(heavy breathing)

38:06.385 --> 38:08.385
(pained grunt,
footsteps crunch)

38:13.825 --> 38:15.992
- (effort grunts)

38:18.397 --> 38:20.997
(grunts, winces in pain)

38:22.801 --> 38:24.734
- Hey, hey, hey, hey.

38:24.736 --> 38:26.970
You okay?
- Yeah. Ah!

38:28.206 --> 38:29.806
(winces in pain)

38:29.875 --> 38:31.808
Those bars,
they're pretty rusty.

38:31.810 --> 38:34.177
I think we can pull a few off.

38:35.314 --> 38:36.946
- Liam, you're burning up.
- No, no.

38:36.982 --> 38:38.615
- You're burning up.

38:39.618 --> 38:41.551
Oh, god.

38:41.553 --> 38:43.720
- (short, sharp breaths)

38:46.224 --> 38:48.224
- I think your rib pierced
your intercostal vein.

38:48.226 --> 38:50.093
- Yeah. Don't worry about me.

38:50.095 --> 38:51.995
- No, no, you're in shock.

38:53.031 --> 38:54.764
Here.

