It's not clean
and it won't last long,

38:56.301 --> 38:58.234
But I need you... I need you
to apply pressure, okay?

38:58.370 --> 38:59.903
I need you to hold
this right here.

39:00.038 --> 39:01.638
- Yeah.
- Okay.

39:01.773 --> 39:03.506
- Yeah.

39:03.508 --> 39:05.342
Hey, jenny...
- Yeah?

