- I love you.
(small laugh)

39:10.782 --> 39:12.449
- I love you, too.
- Mm-hmm.

39:16.388 --> 39:17.987
- Hey, liam? Liam.

39:17.989 --> 39:19.856
- Hey.
- Hi.

39:19.925 --> 39:22.191
- I'm not going anywhere.

39:22.260 --> 39:25.261
- Keep the pressure on, okay?

39:26.231 --> 39:28.598
(grunting with effort)

39:28.600 --> 39:30.366
(grunts) ah!

