Seriously, man!
- What a trio we are, huh?

40:12.844 --> 40:15.512
I won't hurt you, you won't
hurt me, you won't hurt her.

40:15.647 --> 40:17.647
- (shouts) call an ambulance,
you psycho!

40:17.649 --> 40:20.115
Come on!
(fighting grunts)

